Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Somebody will see us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That feels so good, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you're so worried about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you just have to think\Nof me making love to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just clear your mind\Nand only think about our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ltsuke! Uh, l mean, Tagami-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh, you look wonderful as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, l mean, uh,...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l guess the swimming competition is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Our students are training hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:02:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have their sights set on the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope you come out\Nand give them your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tagami-sensei seems kind of down these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Don't be walking around\Nthese hallowed halls wearing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're wearing a jersey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This just happens to be my uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn bloody wench!\NThere's no respect around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe l was a bit too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kawada! Working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, look, it's not ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll show it to you when it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can l give you any advice\Nif l have to wait till it's finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.45,0:03:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let me just take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l said no. Please, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotori...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chitose...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be thinking anything\Nweird about me and Kawada.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. l believe in you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar. l can tell you're accusing\Nme with your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l already know. l heard from Hotori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, l plan on keeping you with my charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm the only one for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, l wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You meany.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder if people will ever find out about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, l'm never going to leave, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's your competition.\NYou do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. You'll come and cheer me on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My god! ls it that time already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mariko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's been a while, Haruhiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. l see that you're still smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was told to quit. But this is one habit\Nl can't quite kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you smoke in front of Chitose as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt seems that Chitose isn't around\Nthe house much these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother's a little worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l told her that young girls like to\Nspend a lot of time with their friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she goes over to your place, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. How long have you known?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On Sunday. She seemed so unusually happy,\Nl was curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitose called you, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l pressed the redial button,\Nand l realized that it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lane No. 5, Kakinouchi Misato-san,\NYamato Swimming Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lane No. 6, Misawa Chitose-san, Seiwa Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get nervous, you just have\Nto think of me making love to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just clear your mind and only think about our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you still remembered my phone number, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do l have to have a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but do you like chatting\Nwith a guy you split up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we did split up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l'm still in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly have a strange way\Nof looking at things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You once said that that's the part of me\Nthat you found most charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't remember what\Nl might have said so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed a bit. What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot's happened to me since we split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't changed at all since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just ask that you take good care of Chitose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if l only see her as some sort of toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l believe in the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so quick to believe in us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the both of you are\Nthe most important people to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just now realized\Nwhy it is that l broke up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's that honesty and trust of yours\Nthat weighed me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hated being thought of like that. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute.\NAren't you going to go see Chitose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Chitose needs is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me strength, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Chitose. Believe in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think only about our love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what should we get her for a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for Rikako's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, today's Chitose's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And l tried so hard.\NOh, maybe he's in the art studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Sensei. What on earth are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawada! What are you hanging around\Na place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason. And l'm not ''hanging around'' either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, hey, perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can help me pick something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to get some clothes\Nor something for a lady friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.26,0:10:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but do you know her size?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use in getting\Nsomething that doesn't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought it was a good idea.\NBut l guess l didn't think it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you at least have a rough idea\Nof her body proportions?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roughly, l suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe we can do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's not bad, but it's kind of bland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l thought it would suit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by the clothes you've been looking at,...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l bet she's around the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, l suppose she's about your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's petite, and very gregarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? For something like that,\Nshe'd need to have a fair-sized chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chest, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a gift for a lady friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the image l have of her so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l bet she'd look good in a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, l think this would suit her perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it looks a bit too sophisticated?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's quite petite, but she's got a good sense of style.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l bet this'll look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kawada.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is the one. Let's decide then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could Onii-chan have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he doesn't care about me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope that Chitose likes this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've been looking for you, Shimotsuki-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The president of the academy wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand you wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've called you all here because we received...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...an anonymous fax addressed to the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The content of this fax is, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just cut to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's about you having relations with one\Nof our female students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ls it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf it's true, then we'll have to\Ndeal with you immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't want the media to latch onto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to have you resign...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so that you don't further damage\Nthe reputation of this academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l believe that would not be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you say that, Tagami-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you just stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that there was no point\Nin us meeting like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.57,0:14:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you explain why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shimotsuki-sensei is a dedicated teacher,...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he is popular among the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fact may have led to misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't find smoke where there's no fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse my private affairs,...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Shimotsuki-sensei and l are engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tagami-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the rumors were true, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Student rumors...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about Shimotsuki-sensei and Tagami-sensei enjoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lunch together on the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:15:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking just one look at you,\Nl knew there had to be a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we hope you carry\Non with your good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Tagami-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to sleep with\Nthe Chairman's only daughter,...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a babe to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l can't believe Tagami-sensei's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you speak out like that, Tagami-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was thinking about a student\Nwith a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was the one who sent that fax.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Misawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the shower room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l said before that l was thinking about\Na student with a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might only be half true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just wanted you, Shimotsuki-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to remain at this academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something the matter with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Telling you something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't come near me. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:17:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't want you to see my face like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope you take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish l hadn't fallen in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why l had to bare my soul today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where on earth did Onii-chan go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so glad you're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard that you won the championship.\NCongratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is for me?
