Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did my sister have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me to take good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mariko's not the type to go blabbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, l guess you still trust my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, please tell me that l'm still yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never hate me or anything, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't ever hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything. Anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then let's celebrate both\Nyour victory and your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Take your clothes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l-l will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, why are you getting all shy\Non me all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do stuff like this with my sister too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first one who l wanted to make my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do what you will to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm tingling all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Onii-chan. Hurry up. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l did say before that this is a double celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thick one is to celebrate your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't do that! Don't put it in me!
