Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't let you off that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.91,0:22:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have something\Nfor your birthday celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:22:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:22:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, Haru. Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.57,0:23:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...! l want to feel you inside of me!
