Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want it harder...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel like l'm going to rip...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.97,0:24:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l just want to feel you all over inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.85,0:24:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm so happy l was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.90,0:24:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onii-chan. Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.28,0:24:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.39,0:25:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You look more sophisticated this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.99,0:25:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.73,0:25:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.50,0:25:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel like doing it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.30,0:25:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly. You're such a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.42,0:25:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onii-chan, how about we go for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.62,0:25:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. lt might be nice seeing\Nthe blossoms at night, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.40,0:25:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Onii-chan. The blossoms are beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.17,0:26:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was always one thing\Nl wanted to beat my sister at.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.37,0:26:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's beautiful, stylish...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.21,0:26:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...very feminine and a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.15,0:26:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you chose me instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.18,0:26:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l love the blossoms at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.79,0:26:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My spirit rises when l stand among\Nthe falling blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.52,0:26:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel like l'm someone other than my usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.33,0:26:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever felt like that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.67,0:26:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chitose...
