Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.75,0:26:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.72,0:26:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we're like this,\Nit's like we're completely naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.30,0:26:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heartbeat, your breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.07,0:27:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your scent, l just love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.50,0:27:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to share the same dreams with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.57,0:27:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Share the same pleasures in life,\Nand the same feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.38,0:27:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l feel like l'm at one with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.75,0:27:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.28,0:27:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because... That's because l love you so much.
